{"tid":463874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門最大的線上賭場「葡京」遭破　6個月經手賭資14.3億","createTime":"2017-11-10T02:40:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T12:03:44.000Z","uid":79563,"like":31,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"c93b7ba4dbaa3432e645c3c1f9a4cb13583e6914","tid":463874,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T02:40:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20171109/1048893.htm?t=澳門最大的線上賭場「葡京」遭破　6個月經手賭資14.3億\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20171109%2F1048893.htm%3Ft%3D%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E7%B7%9A%E4%B8%8A%E8%B3%AD%E5%A0%B4%E3%80%8C%E8%91%A1%E4%BA%AC%E3%80%8D%E9%81%AD%E7%A0%B4%E3%80%806%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E7%B6%93%E6%89%8B%E8%B3%AD%E8%B3%8714.3%E5%84%84&d=8o8IpGvZIrFUzz0L7rZ4FgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=e09fd0f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20171109/1048893.htm?t=澳門最大的線上賭場「葡京」遭破　6個月經手賭資14.3億</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2914/d2914452.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2914%2Fd2914452.jpg&h=9c49e38b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2914/d2914453.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2914%2Fd2914453.jpg&h=50e3e315&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記者柳名耕／台北報導<br />\n<br />\n美國職棒、中華職棒的總冠軍賽、世界大賽在日前先後結束，刑事局偵九大隊偵一隊針對運動簽賭展開清查、掃蕩，在10月30、31日、11月8日前往雲林、嘉義、高雄破獲「葡京娛樂城」，該線上賭場長期在情色片的片頭打廣告，藉以吸收賭客上線簽賭。<br />\n<br />\n警方調查，「葡京娛樂城」長期以線上A片的片頭打廣告，吸引許多賭客購買點數以第三方支付的方式兌換賭資，從2017年4月起開始營業，在短短6個月內經手賭資高達14.3億，不法所得約7000餘萬。<br />\n<br />\n該賭場主嫌黃嘉新（28歲）為了防止警方上門查緝，找了哥哥在新光銀行擔任行員的未婚妻陳菁妤（26歲）作為內應，除了幫忙注意警方是否有行文到銀行查帳戶外，還協助嫌犯到嘉義、雲林、高雄等機房進行網站設定，甚至還協助嫌犯發放賭場成員的薪資。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2914/d2914456.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2914%2Fd2914456.jpg&h=1803ed71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2914/d2914457.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2914%2Fd2914457.jpg&h=d4a9edef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n刑事局偵九大隊偵一隊歷經數月的蒐證後在10月30、31日、11月8日前往嘉義、雲林、高雄等機房查緝，並在機房內查扣電腦22部、手機26支、存摺20本、金融卡20張、教戰守則等贓證物。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，統計帳本後發現2萬3千餘名的會員，每個月大約輸100至900萬間，而該賭場也在半年內獲利7000餘萬，訊後將14名嫌犯依《賭博罪》嫌移送地檢署，其中內應的陳姓行員多了1條《洩漏工商秘密罪》。"},{"pid":"0dd1013443a897594ea096968419bffd2e6b98f3","tid":463874,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T02:41:45.000Z","msg":"以為係強國"},{"pid":"673d9420f066d7e5c67b8db694e3d2a5ae93e260","tid":463874,"uid":5490,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T02:42:00.000Z","msg":"澳門首個....."},{"pid":"142f01eb17b4d09a74b15924373fdb1419490f95","tid":463874,"uid":49004,"like":73,"dislike":3,"score":70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T02:42:25.000Z","msg":"澳門首家線上賭場 下線囉"},{"pid":"336aa4d98c39649e97f3db47169a2b4587f84dab","tid":463874,"uid":24592,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T02:43:46.000Z","msg":"以後唔洗睇廣告了"},{"pid":"561621d80090f44c2bfe756a2dd9569ae5b764b3","tid":463874,"uid":44358,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T02:45:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>澳門首家線上賭場 下線囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來係臺灣扮澳門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b404e6c68c437bea5fe1b0ffb3a69ea71740cb","tid":463874,"uid":92467,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T02:48:35.000Z","msg":"以後睇桃花源論壇啲片源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d7ab92fe7a4bc4b6a124505f87ff6ab958a0538","tid":463874,"uid":34295,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T02:50:29.000Z","msg":"屌哂巴？"},{"pid":"bef6